videos.description: Marquette's Matt Heldt scores via the and-1 play, extending the lead to nine in the first half.
videos.headline: Heldt layup and-1 extends lead for Marquette

videos.description: Tremont Waters buries a deep 3-pointer to cut the Marquette lead to 10 in the first half.
videos.headline: Waters' 3-ball narrows the gap for LSU
